saṃyutta nikāya 45
13. esanāvagga
165. dukkhatāsutta
“tisso imā, bhikkhave, dukkhatā.
katamā tisso?
dukkhadukkhatā, saṅkhāradukkhatā, vipariṇāmadukkhatā—
imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso dukkhatā.
imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ dukkhatānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti.
pañcamaṃ.
